                        <interp inst="t18360509-1158-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>. Aged 24.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Jury and Pro<lb></lb>secutor</hi>. 
